channel.title: StorkPK
channel.description:
Hey guys,
Old school RSCer here from Australia
What ever happened to StorkPK, Will it ever be back? @hixk
Those were the days man, Use to skip school like once every month on a Friday to nerd that shit out for a whole day/night everyday of the weekend. :(
Many memories..
On another note; Is there any server like Stork going around? I remember playing a Replica that sucked diq.
